FOE SAUNDERS LUMBER & HARDWARE COMPANY v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 2409. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Oct. 13, 1941. Pershing, Bosworth, Dick & Dawson, of Denver, Colo., for appellant. James Mcl. Henderson, Sp. Asst, to Atty. Gen., of Denver, Colo., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS and BRATTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellee.
